Data.TextValue: Er is geen print document actie uitgevoerd!

Base.ErrorVariableContents: Fout bij uitvoeren actie voor \\%printer_servername%\%printer_name% met %printer_document_job_id%/%printer_document_job_name%

Base.Explanation: Execute a print job command: pause, restart, resume or delete. The print job is identified by the name of the printer (queue) and the print job id number.

ArrayElement.Name: Printer
ArrayElement.Description: The name of printer or print server queue. Syntax: \\ComputerName\PrinterName. Example: \\SERVER_A\LaserPrinter439

ArrayElement.Name: Job id
ArrayElement.Description: Specify the id number of the target print job. The job id number can be obtained using action 'List printer documents'.

ArrayElement.Name: Pause print job
ArrayElement.Description: Set this property to 'Yes' to pause the print job.

ArrayElement.Name: Restart print job
ArrayElement.Description: Set this property to 'Yes' to restart the print job.

ArrayElement.Name: Resume print job
ArrayElement.Description: Set this property to 'Yes' to resume the print job.

ArrayElement.Name: Delete print job
ArrayElement.Description: Set this property to 'Yes' to delete the print job.

Data.TextValue: De actie is uitgevoerd en voltooid.
